
Carbontool
=========

quick start
-----------

1.- check out the code

3.- install django1.2

    $ pip install django==1.2.4

4.- create the models

    $ cd app && python manage.py syncb

5.- start the server
    
    $ cd app && python manage.py 

6.- point your browser to http://localhost:8000

*extra*

if you want to change application style you will need compass: (probably you need to install ruby and gem before this)

    $ gem install compass

and then:

    $ cd app && compass watch

it will compile every change you do in css_src folder css files
